2. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper deals with the design and analysis of a relay-assisted cellular network, which falls under the scope of networking and internet architecture. 
3. cs.COMM (Communications and Networking): The paper focuses on the performance analysis of a communication system, which is a core area of communications and networking. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with millimeter wave (mmWave) cellular systems, which are used for high-speed multimedia applications. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper analyzes the performance of a complex system involving multiple components, which is relevant to the systems and control field.
